Model Specific Description: This field is used to indicate the earliest known date for the formation of the documented group.
This field is used to indicate the latest known date for the formation of the documented group.
This field is used to indicate the the documented group's location of formation.
This field is used to associate a group which pre-existed the document group and from which it was formed.
This field is used to indicate the earliest known date for the dissolution of the documented group.
This field is used to indicate the latest known date for the dissolution of the documented group.
This field is used to indicate the location of dissolution of the documented group.
